0-d8fb-abff-557a3c9a0000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日，哈马斯性暴力事件引发疯狂的否认主义狂潮</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/the-unhinged-denialist-frenzy-around-hamas-sexual-violence-on-october-7/0000018e-14d0-d2aa-a1be-1dd5f91a0000</link><description>媒体和专家对 10 月 7 日哈马斯性暴力事件进行阴谋性否认，这让他们自己和美国左派蒙羞。但延长加沙战争的呼吁可能会延续针对人质的恐怖行为</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 21:02:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/the-unhinged-denialist-frenzy-around-hamas-sexual-violence-on-october-7/0000018e-14d0-d2aa-a1be-1dd5f91a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在加沙地带南部战斗中丧生； 13人受伤，其中5人伤势严重</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldier-killed-in-south-gaza-strip-fighting-13-wounded-five-seriously/0000018e-157b-d7d3-abce-75fb06720000</link><description>该士兵是参谋军士。 David Sasson，21 岁，来自 Ganot Hadar</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 20:49:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldier-killed-in-south-gaza-strip-fighting-13-wounded-five-seriously/0000018e-157b-d7d3-abce-75fb06720000</guid></item><item><title>一场又一场惨败：梅龙灾难报告还认定内塔尼亚胡对 10 月 7 日有罪</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/one-big-fiasco-mount-meron-disaster-report-also-convicts-netanyahu-for-october-7/0000018e-1508-d2aa-a1be-1dcd1d410000</link><description>该委员会成员对内塔尼亚胡“你不能对你不知道的事情负责”的论点印象不深。一旦预先警告多年的10月7日大屠杀接受调查，他将无法依靠这个辩护</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 19:08:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/one-big-fiasco-mount-meron-disaster-report-also-convicts-netanyahu-for-october-7/0000018e-1508-d2aa-a1be-1dcd1d410000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府：也为暴力侵害妇女的权利而战</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-06/ty-article/.highlight/israels-government-is-fighting-for-the-right-to-be-violent-at-home-too/0000018e-14b0-d8fb-abff-55ba1f630000</link><description>以色列国家安全部长伊塔马尔·本-格维尔（Itamar Ben-Gvir）和他的极右翼政党 Otzma Yehudit 一直在努力剥离女性人口，以减缓进展</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 18:27:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-06/ty-article/.highlight/israels-government-is-fighting-for-the-right-to-be-violent-at-home-too/0000018e-14b0-d8fb-abff-55ba1f630000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的信息 – 第 152 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-152/0000018e-14f6-d1cc-abfe-d7ff963c0000</link><description>哈马斯消息人士称，与以色列的谈判正处于崩溃的边缘。 白宫称，如果哈马斯同意释放所有病人、老人和妇女人质，则可能停火六周。 也门胡塞武装疑似袭击了海湾的一艘商船美国官员表示，亚丁风暴造成“人员伤亡” ■ 战争开始 152 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 18:19:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-152/0000018e-14f6-d1cc-abfe-d7ff963c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列下周允许阿联酋资助的人道主义援助通过海上进入加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/israel-to-allow-entry-via-sea-of-uae-funded-humanitarian-aid-into-gaza-next-week/0000018e-1490-d1cc-abfe-d7bd0ca20000</link><description>当地卫生官员称，海上航线的开通预计将导致国际社会对以色列在加沙的人道主义危机提出更多批评，由于以色列在援助物资转移方面设置困难，迄今为止已有 18 人死亡。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 16:56:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/israel-to-allow-entry-via-sea-of-uae-funded-humanitarian-aid-into-gaza-next-week/0000018e-1490-d1cc-abfe-d7bd0ca20000</guid></item><item><title>尤瓦尔·亚伯拉罕是一位真正的英雄，因为他没有在种族隔离的重压下呻吟</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-03-06/ty-article-opinion/.premium/yuval-abraham-is-actually-a-true-hero-for-not-groaning-under-the-weight-of-apartheid/0000018e-1433-d73e-af9f-7fb7d85a0000</link><description>以色列电影制片人在柏林电影节上的获奖感言似乎冒犯了《国土报》记者的敏感耳朵</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 16:34:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-03-06/ty-article-opinion/.premium/yuval-abraham-is-actually-a-true-hero-for-not-groaning-under-the-weight-of-apartheid/0000018e-1433-d73e-af9f-7fb7d85a0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡和甘茨勉强的政治婚姻显示出稳定的曙光</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-and-gantzs-reluctant-political-marriage-shows-glimpses-of-stability/0000018e-1283-d547-a19e-92935e450000</link><description>本尼·甘茨的美国之行可能羞辱了内塔尼亚胡，但并没有真正威胁到以色列的战时政府 ■ 总理决定允许斋月期间在阿克萨清真寺进行礼拜自由，这表明了政府极右翼势力的局限性</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 16:27:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-and-gantzs-reluctant-political-marriage-shows-glimpses-of-stability/0000018e-1283-d547-a19e-92935e450000</guid></item><item><title>以色列批准在约旦河西岸定居点建造3,476套住房</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/israels-approves-construction-of-3-476-housing-units-in-west-bank-settlements/0000018e-144f-d792-a7be-3cffd18d0000</link><description>一些单位得到了政府的批准，他们称之为对两周前发生的袭击事件的回应，那次袭击造成一名以色列人死亡、11 人受伤。估计显示，今年批准的约旦河西岸住房数量创上世纪九十年代《奥斯陆协议》以来的最高水平</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 16:20:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/israels-approves-construction-of-3-476-housing-units-in-west-bank-settlements/0000018e-144f-d792-a7be-3cffd18d0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的政党驳回了对梅龙灾难的调查结果，称其为“政治挑衅”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-dismisses-probe-findings-into-meron-disaster-labels-it-political-provocation/0000018e-13f7-d7d3-abce-73ffca6d0000</link><description>反对党领袖拉皮德在对 2021 年梅龙灾难（造成 45 名极端正统信徒死亡）的调查结果后猛烈抨击内塔尼亚胡，称如果他是一名普通公民，“他今天就会因过失杀人罪被起诉，并去监狱&amp;#39;</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 15:38:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-dismisses-probe-findings-into-meron-disaster-labels-it-political-provocation/0000018e-13f7-d7d3-abce-73ffca6d0000</guid></item><item><title>复仇、无知和无能：以色列对加沙灾难性的人道主义援助政策</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/vengeance-ignorance-and-incompetence-israels-disastrous-aid-policy-for-gaza/0000018e-13f5-d8fb-abff-57ff1e2d0000</link><description>在战争期间的不同时期，当非以色列媒体已经报道加沙的“饥荒”时，以色列官员仍在将对加沙人的人道主义援助视为“哈马斯的生命线”。在过去的五个月里，以色列从未制定过明确的政策允许物资进入加沙地带</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 14:51:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/vengeance-ignorance-and-incompetence-israels-disastrous-aid-policy-for-gaza/0000018e-13f5-d8fb-abff-57ff1e2d0000</guid></item><item><title>他的书几乎在以色列被禁。但科勒姆·麦肯对巴以冲突仍抱有希望</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-03-06/ty-article-magazine/.premium/author-colum-mccann-wants-to-humanize-the-israeli-palestinian-conflict/0000018e-1322-d950-a18e-f3bb173f0000</link><description>科勒姆·麦肯的小说《Apeirogon》讲述了失去亲人的以色列和巴勒斯坦父亲之间非凡的友谊，现已出版希伯来语版本。作者不确定这是否是一个时机不佳的情况，或者是以色列人阅读他的书的正确时机</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 12:17:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-03-06/ty-article-magazine/.premium/author-colum-mccann-wants-to-humanize-the-israeli-palestinian-conflict/0000018e-1322-d950-a18e-f3bb173f0000</guid></item><item><title>梅龙灾难：内塔尼亚胡“个人负责”，但不应被免职</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/israeli-state-commission-releases-final-report-on-meron-disaster/0000018e-12cd-df16-a58e-1fffe7ad0000</link><description>该国家委员会发现，以色列总理内塔尼亚胡知道或应该知道近三年前在以色列北部梅龙山举行的 Lag B&amp;#39;Omer 庆祝活动期间导致 45 人死亡的危险和风险</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 10:11:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/israeli-state-commission-releases-final-report-on-meron-disaster/0000018e-12cd-df16-a58e-1fffe7ad0000</gui